### ─── HEALTH ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 1. Health check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

###

### ─── AUTH ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 2. Register a new user
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "New User",
  "email": "newuser@finance.com",
  "password": "Test@1234",
  "role": "viewer"
}

###

### 3. Login as Admin  ← copy token into ADMIN_TOKEN below
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@finance.com",
  "password": "Admin@123"
}

###

### 4. Login as Analyst
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "analyst@finance.com",
  "password": "Analyst@123"
}

###

### 5. Login as Viewer
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "viewer@finance.com",
  "password": "Viewer@123"
}

###

### 6. Get own profile
GET http://localhost:3000/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_TOKEN_HERE

###

### ─── RECORDS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 7. List records (paginated)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/records?page=1&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_TOKEN_HERE

###

### 8. Filter by type=income
GET http://localhost:3000/api/records?type=income
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_TOKEN_HERE

###

### 9. Filter by date range
GET http://localhost:3000/api/records?start_date=2025-01-01&end_date=2025-02-28
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_TOKEN_HERE

###

### 10. Filter by category
GET http://localhost:3000/api/records?category_id=1
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_TOKEN_HERE

###

### 11. Search by notes
GET http://localhost:3000/api/records?search=salary
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_TOKEN_HERE

###

### 12. Sort by amount ascending
GET http://localhost:3000/api/records?sort=amount&order=asc
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_TOKEN_HERE

###

### 13. Create record (analyst/admin only)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/records
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "amount": 5000,
  "type": "expense",
  "category_id": 3,
  "date": "2026-04-04",
  "notes": "Team lunch"
}

###

### 14. Get single record (replace ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/records/RECORD_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_TOKEN_HERE

###

### 15. Partial update record (analyst/admin)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/records/RECORD_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "amount": 6000
}

###

### 16. Delete record (admin only — soft delete)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/records/RECORD_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_TOKEN_HERE

###

### 17. Try to create record as Viewer — should return 403
POST http://localhost:3000/api/records
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_VIEWER_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "amount": 100,
  "type": "expense",
  "category_id": 1,
  "date": "2026-04-04"
}

###

### 18. Validation failure — missing required fields
POST http://localhost:3000/api/records
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "type": "expense"
}

###

### ─── DASHBOARD ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 19. Dashboard summary (all roles can view)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/dashboard/summary
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_TOKEN_HERE

###

### ─── USERS ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 20. List users (admin/analyst)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_TOKEN_HERE

###

### 21. Search users by name or email
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users?search=admin
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_TOKEN_HERE

###

### 22. Filter users by role
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users?role=viewer&status=active
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_TOKEN_HERE

###

### 23. Get single user (replace ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users/USER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_TOKEN_HERE

###

### 24. Update user role (admin only)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/users/USER_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "role": "analyst"
}

###

### 25. Deactivate user (admin only — soft delete)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/users/USER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

###

### 26. Try accessing users as Viewer — should return 403
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_VIEWER_TOKEN_HERE

###

### ─── CATEGORIES ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 27. List all categories (any authenticated user)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/categories
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_TOKEN_HERE

###

### 28. Create category (admin only)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/categories
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "name": "Healthcare"
}

###

### 29. Delete category (admin only)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/categories/CATEGORY_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

###

### 30. Try creating category as Viewer — should return 403
POST http://localhost:3000/api/categories
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_VIEWER_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "name": "Blocked"
}

###

### ─── ERROR SCENARIOS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 31. No token — should return 401
GET http://localhost:3000/api/records

###

### 32. Unknown route — should return 404
GET http://localhost:3000/api/doesnotexist

###

### 33. Login with wrong password — should return 401
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@finance.com",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

###
